        "description": "Step into the thrilling world of BAM, the ultimate multiplayer battle game designed for mixed reality (MR). Whether you’re a seasoned gamer or new to the virtual realm, BAM offers a unique and captivating experience that transcends boundaries.\n\nIn BAM, you wield unprecedented control over your battlefield. Set up the tabletop arena anywhere you want, and adjust its scale and rotation. Then take charge of your miniature robot puppeteer-style.\n\nEngage in an adrenaline-pumping fast-paced boxing match. Fire up your jetpack to take the battle up in the air. Collect power-ups to gain special powers, including an innovative “point-to-action” mechanic, offering a fresh perspective on third-person shooting in MR.\n\nBAMs colorful, vibrant arenas pop in every room and are the stage for different game modes. Seize the crown, lose the bomb, or punch your opponents out of the field. Easy-to-master controls and stunning visuals redefine MR gaming, making BAM a must-play experience for all ages.\n\nPlay against AI-bots, or challenge other players all around the world. BAM guarantees instant fun and excitement. Competing against friends in the same room makes BAM the perfect party game.\n\nDive into the future of MR gaming. Enter the electrifying world of BAM.",
